ausforderungen für das Urheberrecht durch Künstliche Intelligenz, z.B. ChatGPT. Wiederholungsfragen sowie ein Anhang zu den höchstrichterlichen Entscheidungen runden das Lehrbuch ab. Außerdem bietet es Rechtsanwälten, die eine Masterausbildung abschließen wollen, eine solide Grundlage für die urheber- und medienrechtliche Ausbildung.  aThis textbook is targeted primarily at students and lawyers specializing in copyright and media law. The new edition deals with the latest rulings from the Federal Court of Justice, the Federal Constitutional Court, the CJEU, and the ECHR, as well as the challenges presented to copyright law by AI, e.g., ChatGPT. The textbook is rounded off with review questions and an appendix on rulings of the highest courts.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 4aDSM-Richtlinie. 4aUrheberrecht. 4aUrheberrechtsrichtlinie. 4aUrhebervertragsrecht.  aCopyright Law Directive.  aDSM Directive.  acopyright contract law.  acopyright law.1 aOstendorff, Saskia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023z9783111318226oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831113251940 cprintz978311132491340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311132509540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111325095423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111325095/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023